description: A small scrap of thermal paper pulled from a spool.
A piece of paper covered in complex weather recordings.  It requires specialized software to interpret.
A piece of paper covered in complex weather recordings.  This one is riddled with visible error messages, but it requires specialized software to interpret.
A piece of paper covered in complex "weather" recordings from the inside of a giant, dead creature.

A piece of paper with data on various local conditions, including weather, radiation, and measurements foreign to you.  The document is coded in a series of overlapping numbers and dots that you cannot understand.  It likely requires specialized software to interpret.
A short sheet of paper.  The document is coded in a series of complex equations and data that you cannot understand.  "CONDITIONS NORMAL" is printed on the bottom.
